										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://accounts.binance.com/register?ref=O0BTS35V" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer">Binance</a> has officially confirmed the launch of the Sealcoin (QAIT) airdrop on Alpha, giving eligible users another opportunity to receive free crypto rewards through the Binance Wallet ecosystem. According to the </span><a href="https://x.com/BinanceWallet/status/2059881406722166911" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400;">announcement</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, the Binance Alpha Sealcoin airdrop will go live on May 28 at 13:00 (UTC). </span></p>
